{"id":15319,"date":"2024-04-25T03:24:03","date_gmt":"2024-04-25T03:24:03","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/sultan@brandsolutions.icu"},"modified":"2025-11-03T05:01:42","modified_gmt":"2025-11-03T05:01:42","password":"","slug":"3rd-party-setup-only-for-user-app","status":"publish","type":"docs","link":"https:\/\/6valley.app\/documentation\/user-app\/3rd-party-setup-only-for-user-app\/","title":{"rendered":"3rd Party Setup"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Google Login<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to enable your Google login then go to <a href=\"https:\/\/console.firebase.google.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/console.firebase.google.com<\/a> and find your project that you have already created for push notification setup then open your <strong>Project-&gt;Authentication-&gt;Sign-in method-&gt; Add new Provider-&gt;Additional providers<\/strong> then select <strong>Google<\/strong> and enable finlay Save.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Android Setup :<\/strong>&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>You need to set a fingerprint in firebase, go to <strong>Project &gt;Project settings &gt; Android apps <\/strong>then select your user app at the bottom you will find<strong> add fingerprint <\/strong>then enter your <strong>SHA1<\/strong> and <strong>SHA256<\/strong> and Save. Visit this site here you will get the instruction how you will get SHA1 and SHA256 <a href=\"https:\/\/developers.google.com\/android\/guides\/client-auth\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Link<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>After publishing on the play store you need to add your <strong>SHA1<\/strong> and <strong>SHA256<\/strong> form App integrity. To found App integrity App signing, go to google play console <strong>Project-&gt; Release &gt; Setup &gt; App integrity &gt; App signing<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Download your <strong>google-service.json<\/strong> file and Copy that file and paste it under <strong>&lt;project&gt;\/android\/app\/<\/strong> folder.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>iOS Setup :<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Go to <a href=\"https:\/\/console.cloud.google.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/console.cloud.google.com<\/a> and select your firebase project, you can find your Client id in, <strong>APIs &amp; Services-&gt; Credentials -&gt; OAuth 2.0 Client IDs<\/strong> then select Web Client and finally copy the Client ID.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Go to <strong>&lt;project&gt;\/ios\/Runner\/Info.plist <\/strong>and add your Client ID<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kevinbatdorf-code-block-pro\" data-code-block-pro-font-family=\"Code-Pro-JetBrains-Mono\" style=\"font-size:.875rem;font-family:Code-Pro-JetBrains-Mono,ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.25rem;--cbp-tab-width:2;tab-size:var(--cbp-tab-width, 2)\"><span style=\"display:block;padding:16px 0 0 16px;margin-bottom:-1px;width:100%;text-align:left;background-color:#2e3440ff\"><svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\"><g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\"><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"><\/circle><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"><\/circle><circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"color:#d8dee9ff;display:none\" aria-label=\"Copy\" class=\"code-block-pro-copy-button\"><pre class=\"code-block-pro-copy-button-pre\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><textarea class=\"code-block-pro-copy-button-textarea\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" readonly>&lt;dict>\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0&lt;key>CFBundleTypeRole&lt;\/key>\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0&lt;string>Editor&lt;\/string>\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0&lt;key>CFBundleURLSchemes&lt;\/key>\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0&lt;array>\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0&lt;string>YOUR_CLIENT_ID&lt;\/string>\n\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0&lt;\/array>\n&lt;\/dict><\/textarea><\/pre><svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" style=\"width:24px;height:24px\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path class=\"with-check\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4\"><\/path><path class=\"without-check\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span><pre class=\"shiki nord\" style=\"background-color: #2e3440ff\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;dict&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;key&gt;<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">CFBundleTypeRole<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;\/key&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;string&gt;<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">Editor<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;\/string&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;key&gt;<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">CFBundleURLSchemes<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;\/key&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;array&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;string&gt;<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">YOUR_CLIENT_ID<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;\/string&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;\/array&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;\/dict&gt;<\/span><\/span><\/code><\/pre><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"How to Do Google Login Setup in 6Valley\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/xrMb7DZSO_E?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Facebook Login<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>If you want to configure facebook login in your project then create your own app form <a href=\"https:\/\/developers.facebook.com\/apps\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/developers.facebook.com\/apps<\/a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Configure your app settings from <strong>App Settings-&gt;Basic<\/strong> with your own Display name, Contact email , Privacy Policy URL, Terms of Service URL, App icon, web app domain<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Add Facebook Login form products section .<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Add your platform (web\/android\/ios) with click Add platform and configure your app.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>To Configuration setting in App Facebook Login-&gt;Settings-&gt;Client OAuth settings enable Client OAuth login, Web OAuth login, Enforce HTTPS, Use Strict Mode for redirect URIs, Login with the JavaScript SDK.<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Also, you need to add your Allowed Domains for the JavaScript SDK (ex-<a href=\"https:\/\/6valley.brandsolutions.icu\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/6valley.brandsolutions.icu<\/a>)&nbsp;<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>To get profile information you need to request access in <strong>App Review-&gt;Permissions and features<\/strong> get access for <strong>public_profile<\/strong><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Now open your flutter project go to <strong>&lt;project&gt;\/lib\/main.dart <\/strong>and replace with your facebook appID<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>For android go to <strong>&lt;project&gt;\/android\/app\/src\/main\/res\/values\/string.xml <\/strong>and set value.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kevinbatdorf-code-block-pro\" data-code-block-pro-font-family=\"Code-Pro-JetBrains-Mono\" style=\"font-size:.875rem;font-family:Code-Pro-JetBrains-Mono,ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.25rem;--cbp-tab-width:2;tab-size:var(--cbp-tab-width, 2)\"><span style=\"display:block;padding:16px 0 0 16px;margin-bottom:-1px;width:100%;text-align:left;background-color:#2e3440ff\"><svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\"><g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\"><circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"><\/circle><circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"><\/circle><circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"><\/circle><\/g><\/svg><\/span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" style=\"color:#d8dee9ff;display:none\" aria-label=\"Copy\" class=\"code-block-pro-copy-button\"><pre class=\"code-block-pro-copy-button-pre\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><textarea class=\"code-block-pro-copy-button-textarea\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-hidden=\"true\" readonly>&lt;resources>\n\u00a0\u00a0&lt;string name=\"app_name\">6valley&lt;\/string>\n\u00a0\u00a0&lt;string name=\"facebook_app_id\">YOUR_APP_ID&lt;\/string>\n\u00a0\u00a0&lt;string name=\"fb_login_protocol_scheme\">fb_YOUR_APP_ID&lt;\/string>\n\u00a0\u00a0&lt;string name=\"facebook_client_token\">Go_to_your_fb_app->Settings->Advance->Security->Client token&lt;\/string>\n&lt;\/resources><\/textarea><\/pre><svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" style=\"width:24px;height:24px\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><path class=\"with-check\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4\"><\/path><path class=\"without-check\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2\"><\/path><\/svg><\/span><pre class=\"shiki nord\" style=\"background-color: #2e3440ff\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;resources&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;string<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> <\/span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">name<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">=<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">app_name<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&gt;<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">6valley<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;\/string&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;string<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> <\/span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">name<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">=<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">facebook_app_id<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&gt;<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">YOUR_APP_ID<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;\/string&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;string<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> <\/span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">name<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">=<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">fb_login_protocol_scheme<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&gt;<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">fb_YOUR_APP_ID<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;\/string&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">\u00a0\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;string<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\"> <\/span><span style=\"color: #8FBCBB\">name<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">=<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color: #A3BE8C\">facebook_client_token<\/span><span style=\"color: #ECEFF4\">&quot;<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&gt;<\/span><span style=\"color: #D8DEE9FF\">Go_to_your_fb_app-&gt;Settings-&gt;Advance-&gt;Security-&gt;Client token<\/span><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;\/string&gt;<\/span><\/span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #81A1C1\">&lt;\/resources&gt;<\/span><\/span><\/code><\/pre><\/div>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>For ios go to <strong>ios\/Runner\/Info.plist<\/strong> and set value<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kevinbatdorf-code-block-pro\" data-code-block-pro-font-family=\"Code-Pro-JetBrains-Mono\" style=\"font-size:.875rem;font-family:Code-Pro-JetBrains-Mono,ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,Monaco,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.25rem;--cbp-tab-width:2;tab-size:var(--cbp-tab-width, 2)\"><span style=\"display:block;padding:16px 0 0 16px;margin-bottom:-1px;width:100%;text-align:left;background-color:#2e3440ff\"><svg xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\"